PrecisAcceptance of a Resolution approved at a General Meeting of the Fraser Lake Band of Indians on January 20, 1988, at which time the Band voted in favour of the revocation of a Surrender dated March 1, 1959 (P.C.1959-344), which provided for the leasing of the whole of Canyon Lake Indian Reserve No. 7, in the Province of British Columbia.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of a Resolution approved at a General Meeting of the Fraser
Lake Band of Indians on January 20, 1988, at which time the Band voted in
favour of the revocation of a Surrender dated March 1, 1959
(P.C.1959-344), which provided for the leasing of the whole of Canyon
Lake Indian Reserve No. 7, in the Province of British Columbia.
